                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#132v">f. 132v</locus>
                           <desc>: Note on types and qualities of precious stones.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#132v">132v</locus>: እጽሕፍ: ነገረ: አዕናቍ: ቀይሐን: ወኅብረ: ደም:
                              ወጸዓዳን: ወሐመልሚላን: ወኅብረ: ስሞሙሂ: ጳዝዮን: … </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#132v">132v</locus>: I write the account of precious
                              stones: red ones, those like blood, white ones, green ones, and there
                              common name is Ṗazǝyon …</quote>
                           <note> The note is written in the same hand as Additio 2. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#132v">f. 132v</locus>
                           <desc>: Note on symbolic interpretation of Biblical peoples as different
                              animals. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#132v">132v</locus>: ምሳሌ: አሕዛብ: አናብስት: ባቢሎን: አናምርት:
                              ሚዶን: ድብ: ፋርስ: አዝዕብት: ግብጽ: አክልብት: ኢሎፍሊ: … </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#132v">132v</locus>: Symbolic interpretation of
                              peoples: Babylon (is like) Lion, Midon (is like) tigers, Persia
                              (is like) bear, Egypt (is like) hyenas, Philistines (ʾIlofli)
                              (are like) dogs … </quote>
                           <note> The note is written in the same hand as Additio 1. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of Text I is crudely written on the front
                           board with yellow paint.
 - Corrections written interlineally: <locus target="#7v">7v</locus>, 8r, 28v, 29r, 53r.
